Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次來還是兩年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說他們會爽快地答應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道是為重建木葉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會助我們一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂忍術就是挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你們所知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在村裡人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此D級任務便下放給下忍執行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是凱老師 小李還在住院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能組成二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被原本的編組束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此調入了一名新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快看吧 新面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是新面孔了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的新面孔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還期待會出現帥一點的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是對不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回和鳴人組成三人小組 執行D級任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我是濃眉的替身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心小李
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一有空就會去看他的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了 年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們的任務是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況記載在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回任務的隊長是天天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都是寧次當隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為本次任務由天天來擔當最為妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸君 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師 就這樣丟下我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面怎麼辦 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦 我是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看讓寧次做隊長不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天被選作隊長的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 這只是D級任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼各方面都感覺怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那間屋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 木葉忍具研究室分部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說原本是在木葉村裡的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦無1000只 手裡劍1000只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還有其他新忍具一併帶回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 要那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人哪拿的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個任務的隊長還真非天天莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天的卷軸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通過時空間忍術收納各式各樣的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後根據需要召喚出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時…時空間忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈術總知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它當作忍具版就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去時可以兩手空空了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新研製的忍具會是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂忍術就是挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 新忍具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪兒不對勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是硫黃師傅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是硫黃 你們是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是村裡派來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有新忍具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新忍具不是順帶的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是隊長的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝石 去把那個拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸刃苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸刃苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下都做成刀刃 提升殺傷力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 刀刃上塗有劇毒 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的太遲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣使用者的風險也很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我又做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸手苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這沒什麼用吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千刃手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿都拿不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀不連之鐮刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是半吊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒一個能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其它忍具了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不喜歡這些小玩意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給你們看看大傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢伙 請務必讓我見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它了 忍者手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 跟我換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由忍者自由操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠隨心所欲自由飛行的手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在所握的是操縱桿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果將它向左或向右扭轉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱桿 控制操縱桿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其它的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現階段就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之所以被村子趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為盡製造這些爆炸性的失敗實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是失敗 是挑戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打算否認嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要什麼新忍具了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需提供普通的苦無1000只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的手裡劍1000只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給村子就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要什麼普通的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我老實去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊啊 硝石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是無趣呢 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你們做些普通的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失望什麼呢 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還對新忍具有所期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱班的三人都是近戰忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一個人以遠程掩護為主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是討厭掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能得到我專屬的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就能更接近一些作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子衝上去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣單純真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你說的也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚都快焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上硫黃師傅他們一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔他們真不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確都是些不中用的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但耗費在這些發明上的熱情卻是貨真價實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為硫黃師傅會扔下實驗室潛逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 替我勘察下四周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來就在這前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼明顯的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我毀了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎啊 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部命中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把刀刃的黑澤以及這個設計
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些 那些 都是超完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想把所有的都帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 寧次 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件不留地全給我搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能不能都放進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 紋絲不動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自搬動我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將這裡的忍具分給村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶刀貴在持刀者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想我的忍具被人糟蹋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真通過了那些機關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在進行忍具的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個剛開發出來的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我的傑作忍具 地團太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地團太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不小心就踩中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 賀目流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我們只是想分些忍具用用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隸屬木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能將忍具給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉現在亂得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連國境都輕而易舉地穿過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硫黃師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此 楠根
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是些小屁孩的三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉還真是人手短缺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次攻左 鳴人攻右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邊保護硫黃師傅邊替你們掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 楠根
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是我的試驗品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇行和鶴龜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會落在他們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 硝石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅靠村子的研究資金不夠支付實驗費用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好瞞著老師將一些忍具給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說對方不過是些忍具迷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那些只不過是試驗品就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器早晚都是用於戰場的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且即便是試驗品 那也是我做出來的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇行是伸縮自如 柔韌有餘的十文字搶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴龜中暗藏著裝載忍具的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些忍具的弱點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是試驗品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們之所以稱為試驗品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因我開發出了比它們更為強大的忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將那個交給我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是…地團太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來近戰能力不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離拉開後不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我來對付你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地團太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑蠻力可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要用技巧才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的新作品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老實些拱手相讓的話 就留你們一條小命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能動粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從你開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再毫無作為可大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是隊長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來槍彈用盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 鳴人 給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用手柄進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的槍一樣 伸縮自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆 這裡就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆 爆 爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算借助爆炸的反作用力來操縱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但利用爆風驅使了鐵球行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還將其當成防禦壁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋住它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地團太被你耍得淋漓盡致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硫黃師傅 這地團太就歸我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了地團太的不足之處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝石 趕快進行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我回收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個了不起的忍具使者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的寶物任你挑選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務成功了啊 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼失望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 你可是出盡了風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地團太要是改造完畢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是零號演習場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊抓住那些混蛋鴕鳥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要戰鬥到底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你們有沒有共同執行過任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先執行任務吧
